## Application Source Code (Private)

The application source code has been moved to a private repository 
to reflect real-world security practices.

Core components included in this project:

- .NET microservices containerized with Docker
- Kubernetes deployments running on Amazon EKS
- GitHub Actions CI/CD pipeline
- DockerHub container registry
- Amazon RDS PostgreSQL database
- NGINX / ALB Ingress for traffic routing
- Prometheus + Grafana monitoring stack
- Terraform infrastructure provisioning

If required, access can be provided upon request.
